# API DESIGN DOCUMENTATION

This document is the specification for an accounting backend service.

## Endpoints

The following endpoints will be exposed on the backend

## Create User

This endpoint is used for creating users on the system

| Name | Value |
| ---- | ----- |
| Endpoint | /api/v1/users |
| Method | POST |
| Authorization | None |

### Create User Request Attributes

| Name | Description | Data Type | Required |
| ---- | ----------- | --------- | -------- |
| firstName | first name of the user | string | true |
| lastName | last name of the user | string | true |
| email | email address of the user | string | true |
| password | password for securing user account | string | true |

### Create User sample request

``` JSON
{
  "firstName": "Bender",
  "lastName": "Rodriguez",
  "email": "bender@futur.ama",
  "password": "password"
}
```

### Create User Response Attributes

| Name | Description | Data Type | Required |
| ---- | ----------- | --------- | -------- |
| userId | primary identifier of the user | integer | true |
| token | authorization token to be used for protected endpoints | string | true |

### Create User sample response

``` JSON
{
  "userId": 1,
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6ImJlbmRlckBmdXR1ci5hbWEiLCJmaXJzdE5hbWUiOiJCZW5kZXIiLCJsYXN0TmFtZSI6IlJvZHJpZ3VleiIsImlhdCI6MTUxNjIzOTAyMn0.iE9UIgEhoWZQuHmCFuT1EeQ9Jdo1F-Q7yinqXTfgPeY"
}
```

## Create Account

This endpoint is used for creating accounts on the system

| Name | Value |
| ---- | ----- |
| Endpoint | /api/v1/accounts |
| Method | POST |
| Authorization | None |

### Create Account Request Attributes

| Name | Description | Data Type | Required |
| ---- | ----------- | --------- | -------- |
| userId | id of the user creating the account | integer | true |
| openingBalance | starting balance for the new account | float | false |

### Create Account sample request

``` JSON
{
  "userId": 1,
  "openingBalance": 1000
}
```

| Name | Description | Data Type | Required |
| ---- | ----------- | --------- | -------- |
| accountId | id of the new account | integer | true |
| balance | starting balance for the new account | float | false |

### Create Account sample response

``` JSON
{
  "accountId": 1,
  "balance": 1000
}
```
